io.requery.proxy

Class EntityProxy<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.requery.proxy.EntityProxy<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - entity type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Gettable<E>, Settable<E>

    public class EntityProxy<E>
extends Object
implements Gettable<E>, Settable<E>
    Proxy object for a data entity containing various properties that can be read or written and the Attribute meta data associated with them.
